  "history-01": {
    "1": { correct: "a", correctText: "1 only", exp: "Stone Age periods are identified by the type and technology of tools (1, correct). Statement 2 is wrong — there ARE regional variations in tool technology — and statement 3 is wrong — cultures did not evolve uniformly/unilinearly across the subcontinent. Hence 1 only." },
