    "4": { correct: "b", correctText: "2 only", exp: "Statement 2 is correct — V.S. Wakankar spotted the Bhimbetka rocks from a train and discovered the paintings. Statement 1 is wrong — the first Indian rock paintings (Sohagighat) were reported by Archibald Carlleyle, not “Alexander Burns.” Statement 3 about Orissa rock art is inaccurate. Hence 2 only." },
