    "6": { correct: "c", correctText: "Vicinity of Thamirabarani river", exp: "Recent excavations (Sivakalai/Adichanallur) near the Thamirabarani river in Tamil Nadu revealed a flourishing agrarian society with rice cultivation by ~1200 BCE. The Raichur Doab, Vamsadhara and Krishna delta are not the sites of this finding." },
