    "352": { correct: "b", correctText: "The Talukdars were interlopers with no permanent stakes in the land.", exp: "The Summary Settlement of 1856 (in Awadh) assumed the talukdars were interlopers without permanent stakes, and sought to settle directly with the cultivators — alienating the talukdars (a cause of 1857). Hence option (b)." },
